  dialogue:
  - '"ONE, what''s that?"

'
  - '"There''s a crack in the ground, be careful Eva!"'
  - '"Wait ONE, I think I see something glowing down there! Could we check it out?"'
  - You pause for a second. Knowing that HUE could catch up any moment, it is hard
    to say yes. But maybe Eva could be right about something. And she doesn't have
    much time left...
  responses:
  - responseText: Explore
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1c93a13196fd376448ff6bdfedf41af5, type: 2}
  - responseText: Don't Explore
